abstract: >
  A fully customizable AI chatbot template built with modern web technologies.
  This project allows developers to easily tailor the appearance, behavior, and AI integrations 
  of a chatbot. It supports advanced technologies such as Next.js, Tailwind CSS, RAG, Pinecone, 
  and multiple AI APIs (OpenAI, Fireworks AI, Anthropic AI), enabling rapid deployment 
  and customization for various use cases including personal assistants, FAQ bots, 
  research assistants, and educational tools.
